INTERSECT
INTERSECT DISTINCT 算子下面直接接着 PX COORDINATOR 或者 EXCHANGE 的情况，会在 EXCHANGE 下面分配一个 DISTINCT
会下推
select c1 from lyqtest1 INTERSECT select c1 from lyqtest2;
+------+
| c1   |
+------+
|    1 |
|    2 |
+------+
